  "title": "RS_TMSEEG_Data",
  "description": "This dataset comprises transcranial magnetic stimulation (TMS) concurrent with electroencephalography (EEG) recordings collected to develop and validate quantitative methods for identifying site- and stimulation-specific TMS-evoked potentials. The study presents a cosine similarity metric approach for characterizing TMS-EEG responses, with potential applications in non-invasive brain stimulation research and clinical neurophysiology.",
